{
  "stem": "8892.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I mean, this was so fast and so organized that I cannot tell you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And, of course, you see women soldier.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were women soldier, German Aufseherinnen, they called them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Soldier run and hollering.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And some already probably talking Hungarian, somebody in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we're lining up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then our main concern-- to stick together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So when one sit on a chair, I think my sister stood there till I get off that chair, all shaven, naked, standing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And then you went into a shower.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So I'm coming out of the shower.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "At least we washed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they threw us-- [SIGHS] I had a green, like, a crepe dress to my ankle.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I mean, in the showers, we started laughing because we looked so hideous, all of us, that, that I-- it's unspeakable.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "You couldn't-- you couldn't even imagine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And hundreds and hundreds of women, small, short, young, old, all naked, and all shaven-- nobody knew nothing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But we sort of cling together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And we watched.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Then again, when you form a line, that's a five-- it's going to be.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So we were shaven.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And then we were taken in an huge barracks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And we stayed there overnight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I think it was called Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I don't even know where we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "The next morning, dawn came. 5 o'clock, we have to be out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "They're counting us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Again, form a line with five of us, with the clothing what they give us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And, and then they give us that little, like the army's guy has, you know, the little kettle for the food.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And they give you a spoon and fork attached to it, from metal, whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And we form a line.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And we're going to get breakfast.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
